			<a class="tooltip" href="#">
				<img src="images/help.png" align="left" />What is RSS?
				<span>
					RSS feeds enable web sites to tell you when they have new articles.
					Instead of constantly visiting your favorite web sites to find out what's new, you simply <strong>subscribe</strong> to them in your RSS reader, and new articles come to you automatically.
					<br /><br />
					Unlike email, RSS is <strong>private</strong> - the sites you subscribe to know nothing about you.
				</span>
			</a>
